Dear GSU-UE bargaining unit members=2C

I am writing to you because MIT has received many questions concerning the=
 new leaves policies in the MIT & MIT-GSU collective bargaining agreement=
 (CBA).

Types of leave include=2C among others=2C sick time=2C family and medical=
 leave=2C childbirth and parental accommodation=2C and vacation time. The=
 leave policies in the CBA apply to students who are serving in full or pa=
rtial RA=2C TA=2C or Instructor-G appointments.

Students on full fellowships should arrange for flexibility and/or time aw=
ay from academic responsibilities as they have done in the past=2C by work=
